42.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business Trends Graphs and charts. Dollar sign with rocket\" data-id=\"1305707642\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8000px\" height=\"4500px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305707642/image_1305707642.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305707642/image_1305707642.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305707642/image_1305707642.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305707642/image_1305707642.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305707642/image_1305707642.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305707642/image_1305707642.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305707642/image_1305707642.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305707642/image_1305707642.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Vertigo3d</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Average Annual Total Returns for Class Y Shares</strong></p> <span class=\"table-responsive\"><span class=\"table-scroll-wrapper\"><span data-intersection-boundary=\"start\"></span><table> <tr> <td> </td> <td><p><strong>Month-to- Date</strong></p></td> <td><p><strong>Quarter- to-Date</strong></p></td> <td><p><strong>Year-to- Date</strong></p></td> <td><p><strong>1-Year</strong></p></td> <td><p><strong>3-Years</strong></p></td> <td><p><strong>5-Years</strong></p></td> <td><p><strong>10-Years</strong></p></td> </tr> <tr> <td><p><strong>Pioneer Disciplined Growth Fund (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">MUTF:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INYDX\" title=\"Pioneer Disciplined Growth Fund Inst\">INYDX</a></span>)</strong></p></td> <td><p>2.29%</p></td> <td><p>5.06%</p></td> <td><p>16.56%</p></td> <td><p>30.22%</p></td> <td><p>9.65%</p></td> <td><p>16.88%</p></td> <td><p>13.88%</p></td> </tr> <tr> <td><p><strong>Russell 1000 Growth Index (Benchmark)</strong> <strong>1</strong></p></td> </tr> </table> </span></span>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1305707642/image_1305707642.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743589-pioneer-disciplined-growth-fund-q3-2024-performance-and-market-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 18:41:00"}, {"id": "4743611", "title": "Roots Corporation 2024 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Roots Corporation in conjunction with their 2024 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106116\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743611-roots-corporation-2024-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 18:34:50"}, {"id": "4743602", "title": "November CPI In Line, Fed Expected To Cut Rates Next Week", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165462299/image_2165462299.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Woman shopping at a convenience store and checking her receipt\" data-id=\"2165462299\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165462299/image_2165462299.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165462299/image_2165462299.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165462299/image_2165462299.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165462299/image_2165462299.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165462299/image_2165462299.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165462299/image_2165462299.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165462299/image_2165462299.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165462299/image_2165462299.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Hispanolistic</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><a href=\"https://www.bls.gov/news.release/archives/cpi_12112024.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">November CPI</a> verified right in line with expectations, emboldening the Fed to cut rates next week. The Headline rate was 0.30% while the Core rate rose by the same (+0.31%). You have to go back to February and March to find higher rates</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165462299/image_2165462299.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743602-november-cpi-in-line-fed-expected-to-cut-rates-next-week", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 18:30:46"}, {"id": "4743583", "title": "CAVA Group: Insiders Deep Six Their Stock At 200x P/E -- You Should, Too", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1342399503/image_1342399503.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Words Insider Selling on yellow finance background from graphs, charts. Trend Up and Down. 3D render\" data-id=\"1342399503\" data-type=\"getty-image\"